contentOfChat: This is the Announcements channel.  Messsages with important information related to Injector or Chatbox will be posted here.
Chatbox update 2.1.0: Removed "2" in Chatbox2, added Channels and Important Channels, added Admin system, chatlog no longer cleared on server restart
Chatbox update 2.1.1: Made the time indicators readable
Chatbox update 2.2.0: We have Direct Messaging now! Use the black search bar on the left to search for a user, then click on their name to start or read your DMs with them.
